result.execSummary:
The defendant Treena A Rose was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Treena A Rose is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Treena A Rose was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct. This is not a criminal offense and results only in a money penalty for this offense.
